---
title: Hot Smoked Salmon Spaghetti with Crispy Roasted Broccoli
description: We're thinking pink today. Salmon pink. Not only is this fish delicious, it's packed to the gills with omega 3 fatty acids which have been shown to have benefits for both brain function and blood pressure. So dinner can be good for the head and the heart - and the taste buds of course. Enjoy!
